  <div id="sidebar">
    <p>If you are creating commercial EPUBs in volume, you should <a href="http://blog.threepress.org/2010/12/16/running-epubcheck-on-your-computer/">install epubcheck</a> instead of using this tool.</p>

    <p>This validator uses <a href="http://code.google.com/p/epubcheck/">epubcheck 1.1 and epubpreflight 0.1.0</a></p>
    <p>Once you have validated your document, consider uploading it to <a href="http://ibisreader.com/">Ibis Reader</a> to view it in our highly-conformant EPUB reader.
    </p>
